      <title>BP承诺在Elliott的干预后“重置”策略“重置”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/bp-ceo-pledges-strategy-reset-after-intervention-of-activist</link>
      <description><![CDATA[BP PLC在报告利润急剧下降后，在即将进行的战略更新中承诺了重大变化，因为该公司试图扭转延长的表现不佳时期，现在已经在激进主义者Elliott Investment Management中提取了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/bp-ceo-pledges-strategy-reset-after-intervention-of-activist</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 07:08:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其说，在对交易的需求混合需求之后，将权衡IPO放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/turkey-said-to-weigh-ipo-slowdown-after-mixed-demand-for-deals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位熟悉讨论的人说，土耳其正在考虑放慢伊斯坦布尔主要餐厅的首次公开发行速度，因为投资者对最近的一批交易的需求混合了要求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/turkey-said-to-weigh-ipo-slowdown-after-mixed-demand-for-deals</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 07:03:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非简化了与州达到1.08亿美元的交易规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/south-africa-eases-rules-for-deals-with-state-under-108-million</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非颁布了其公共筹集法律的变更，该法律将减少价值不到20亿兰特（1.08亿美元）的项目的繁文tape节，政府与私人企业合作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/south-africa-eases-rules-for-deals-with-state-under-108-million</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 07:03:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
